
## Software design
Keylogger malware application designed in c++.  C++ windows app traces all the keyboard inputs from the user and record 
 it into a text file. The app sends the text files to a gmail account. We  used Windows Powershell to do it. 


## User story 

Scenario: Parents supervise their children
          Given that we are parents
          When we install the program to children computers
          Then we must track the users’ activities 
Scenario: Monitor what employees are doing
         Given that I am employer
         When I install the program to the employees’ computers
         Then  I can observe employees computer activities
Scenario: Security reasons
         Given that I am employee 
         When I am using keylogger program
         Then I track the input of key words and phrases associated with commercial information which could damage the company 
